It is possible to manage assortments linked to trade conditions. 

The promotion does not trigger at the individual line level but on the total document. The system checks that all assortment-level conditions are met and then applies a discount. 

The "Assortment Code" field must be set within the "Documents" tab in the Sales Discount table for a specific customer or customer group in relation to the parameters set in the "Customers" tab.

